                                                                                    SampleStore™ II -20°C to RT Automated Sample Storage
                                                                                




SampleStore II is designed for reliability, storage density and with a modular architecture to maximize adaptability. SampleStore II offers you the expertise we’ve gained from 20 years of developing automated sample storage products for biobanking applications that range from compound storage for drug discovery to DNA and blood serum storage.













